       <Markdown>
            # Writing Survey 2
            ## Goals I Set For My Writing
            
            At this point you will reflect on the kinds of goals you usually set for yourself
            as a writer. To probe your self-understanding, you will be presented with a series
            of statements and asked to indicate whether you (a) strongly agree, (b) agree, 
            (c) disagree, or (d) strongly disagree with that statement. Work your way through
            these statements, picking the answer that seems to match your own experience and
            feelings best. There are quite a few statements to get through, so don't take too
            much time on any single statement. When you are done, you will have a chance to
            read a computer-generated summary of your answers. 

       </Markdown>
    </Vertical>
