                   Our data is: 
                   <Ref id="ws2_ref6" target="ws2_goals_1" />
                   <Ref id="ws2_ref7" target="ws2_goals_2" />
                   <Ref id="ws2_ref8" target="ws2_goals_3" />
                   <Ref id="ws2_ref9" target="ws2_goals_4" />
